Revision history for File-PlainPath

0.030     2013-11-06
        Directory separators can now be lexically scoped.

0.020   2012-02-27
        Directory separators can now be set on a per-package basis.

0.011   2012-02-26
        Added support for multiple path arguments in the path() method.

0.01    2012-02-26
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
